AddressInfo.Title: Buckland Kent St
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Access Kent St, by turning into Buckland Rd from Tasman Hwy.

Connections.Comments: Payment with Wevolt App. Public toilets and park located 300m away on corner of Burnett and East Streets Buckland. Buckland Inn (Pub) only 130m away. Historical Buckland General Store is not operating. Storekeepers Boutique accommodation adjacent.

GeneralComments: Depending on charge point location, there is room to pull and charge when towing a trailer.
